Release Checklist
=================
* Ensure Constants.DEBUG is set to false

Release Workflow
================
```
    git checkout glimmr-l
    git cherry-pick master..dev
    mvn release:clean release:prepare release:perform
    # <Manually bump versionCode and versionName in AndroidManifest.xml>
    # (maven bumps them as part of release but doesn't retain the changes)

    git checkout dev
    mvn release:clean release:prepare release:perform
    # <Manually bump versionCode and versionName in AndroidManifest.xml>
    # (maven bumps them as part of release but doesn't retain the changes)

    git checkout master
    git merge dev --no-ff
    git push --all
```
